---
By: Isaac of Syria
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 152
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Faith
---
As soon as a man rejects all visible help and human hope, and follows after
God with faith and a pure heart, grace straightaway follows after him and
reveals its power in help of various kinds.
